{"tid":2289444,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"公會：新巴確認不再提供法律支援　已另覓律師代表","createTime":"2020-11-17T09:09:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-17T11:35:08.000Z","uid":56115,"like":9,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"3f9bf4d5622bd4239f14d02d86ec909d451d9129","tid":2289444,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T09:09:03.000Z","msg":"有網民於 9月 6 日發起九龍遊行，期間警方於彌敦道截停一部 970 號新巴，36 歲車長被警指「無故響號」、駕駛巴士「快速行駛」貼近警員而被捕，最終遭控一項不小心駕駛罪。案件今午（17 日）在九龍城裁判法院再提訊，車長仍毋須答辯，案件押後至 12 月 29 日，以待控方諮詢法律意見，期間他續准保釋。另外，新巴職工會會長林錦標今在庭外表示，公司已確認不再向車長提供法律支援，工會已另覓律師團隊協助車長，是次提訊已由另一律師代表車長。"},{"pid":"46097ee445f1ce783659e1e9d39de1b0e01d9fad","tid":2289444,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T09:09:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E8%BB%8A%E9%95%B7%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E4%B8%8D%E5%B0%8F%E5%BF%83%E9%A7%95%E9%A7%9B-%E6%A1%88%E4%BB%B6%E5%86%8D%E6%8A%BC%E5%BE%8C-%E5%B7%A5%E6%9C%83-%E6%96%B0%E5%B7%B4%E7%A2%BA%E8%AA%8D%E4%B8%8D%E5%86%8D%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E6%94%AF%E6%8F%B4-%E5%B7%B2%E5%8F%A6%E8%A6%93%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E8%25BB%258A%25E9%2595%25B7%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25BF%2583%25E9%25A7%2595%25E9%25A7%259B-%25E6%25A1%2588%25E4%25BB%25B6%25E5%2586%258D%25E6%258A%25BC%25E5%25BE%258C-%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E6%259C%2583-%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25AA%258D%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2586%258D%25E6%258F%2590%25E4%25BE%259B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25BE%258B%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258F%25B4-%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E5%258F%25A6%25E8%25A6%2593%25E5%25BE%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E8%25A1%25A8%2F&d=gkHqMR5YDMJAUJmZ80XM4wfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=23855e7d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E8%25BB%258A%25E9%2595%25B7%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25B